title: Has anyone noticed Google photos video editors disappeared?!
content:
It's weird that I had the new video editors in my pixel 5 last week and now they all disappeared! I talked with google chat support and they asked to update the app, clear cache, restart, uninstall update and update again but none worked. I noticed it's not my case only as below link:
https://www.reddit.com/r/GooglePixel/comments/m5s1cq/google_photos_video_editing/?utm_source=amp&utm_medium=&utm_content=post_body
